 Protos right hand is blow off. Sparks shoot out. He snarls in the bots 
direction. He then turns into Galvatrons robot mode. The tail swung back and 
forth. The left hand still absent and sparking. He  puled the blue flamed 
sword with his right and flew upwards begging the bot to follow.
